C1:
In the year 2XXX,
You command a ship on an expedition to harvest rare metals
It's been 1 week since you've departed Earth, and you decide
to mine in an asteroid feild nearby
C2:
As you explore the asteroid feild, you fail to see an asteroid
headed your way. The asteroid hits your ship head on and drains
the extra fuel tank that was reserved for the passage back to Earth
C3:
You have to rely on your remaining power to navigate yourself back home
